<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١٨٦-<span class="c5"> أَخْبَرَنِي حَرْبُ بْنُ إِسْمَاعِيلَ قَالَ:</span> سَأَلْتُ أَحْمَدَ قُلْتُ:<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>رَجُلٌ أَوْصَى بِسَهْمٍ مَنْ مَالِهِ لِرَجُلٍ كَمْ يُعْطَى؟<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ:</span> السِّهَامُ عِنْدَنَا عَلَى سِتَّةٍ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">قُلْتُ:</span> يُعْطَى السُّدُسَ؟<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ:</span> نَعَمْ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>